<div class="com-share" data-id="24114" data-title="《「万物简史」海外华人爱“闷声发大财”？》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/24114/medium/24114.jpg?1458286202" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/24114.html" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
